            <title>[MAHOUT-1482] Rework quickstart website</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1482</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our quickstart website must be much more helpful.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should describe how to add Mahout as maven dependency to a Java project and how to start working on the source code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mahout.apache.org/users/basics/quickstart.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://mahout.apache.org/users/basics/quickstart.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
